      <h1>Best Robo-Advisors (2026) &mdash; Fees, Features &amp; Performance Compared</h1>
      <p class="article-intro">Robo-advisors have fundamentally changed how people invest. By using algorithms to build, manage, and rebalance diversified portfolios of low-cost ETFs, these platforms deliver institutional-quality investment management for a fraction of the cost of a traditional financial advisor. Whether you are investing your first $500 or managing a $500,000 portfolio, a robo-advisor can automate the entire process &mdash; from asset allocation and rebalancing to tax-loss harvesting &mdash; for as little as 0.25 percent per year. In this comprehensive comparison, we evaluate the eight leading robo-advisors in 2026 on fees, features, performance, and who each platform is best suited for. Use our <a href="/financial-calculators/investment-calculator/">investment calculator</a> to project how your portfolio could grow over time.</p>
    </header>

